### ==========================================
### 💬 CHAT ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================
### Note: Chat only works after a bid is accepted on a project.
### Login as either the client or the accepted freelancer.

### Load Chat History for a Project
GET http://localhost:6868/api/chat/PROJECT_ID_HERE

###

### Send a Message
POST http://localhost:6868/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "projectId": "PROJECT_ID_HERE",
    "receiverId": "RECEIVER_USER_ID_HERE",
    "text": "Hey! I just accepted your bid. Let's discuss the project details."
}

###

### Send Reply (login as the other user)
POST http://localhost:6868/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "projectId": "PROJECT_ID_HERE",
    "receiverId": "RECEIVER_USER_ID_HERE",
    "text": "Thanks for accepting! I'll start working on the wireframes today."
}

###

### Mark All Messages as Read in a Project Chat
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/chat/PROJECT_ID_HERE/read

###
